......in the Dragon's home - in Seli's room - her warm bed I place her.  Hanging her magic crystal back in the window....Amber under her armm tucking them both under a blanket that Deknyr made of crystalline silk ....I curl up in the rockin chair beside Seli's bed, and softly I begin to hum....<br>
